&lt;li&gt;Driving complex technical decisions across console performance and low-level systems architecture, with reach into graphics, tooling, and engine infrastructure to ensure our systems scale for both developers and players.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborating with internal and external leads to advance engine platform capabilities — including console features, anti-cheat, and team workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
